#### Neuro-Symbolic Guardians
```python
from strands import Agent, Hook

# Define a rule hook
def booking_rule_hook(params):
    if params['guests'] > 10:
        raise ValueError("Maximum guest limit exceeded")

# Register the hook
agent = Agent()
agent.register_hook(Hook.BEFORE_TOOL_CALL, booking_rule_hook)
```

